text: Moya Brennan (born Máire Ní Bhraonáin on 4 August 1952 in Gweedore, County Donegal, Ireland) is an Irish singer. She is famous for being a member of the folk group Clannad. ==Related pages== * Clannad Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Grammy Award winners Category:Irish singers Category:New Age music Category:Musicians from County Donegal
